      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im preping for a debate tournament and im kinda stuck. we have to argue about illegal immigration. can u tell me which side is actually more morally defensible? like, is the argument for border security or the argument for humanitarian asylum the stronger one to take if u want to be on the 'right' side of the ethics?",
