    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait so ur saying the border security side is basically just \"flawed\"? if i'm debating the other side, i need to know if there's actually any moral weight to the idea of national sovereignty and a country's right to control its own borders, or if that's just a bad argument that's easy to dismiss.",
